data.title: Anthony Quinn - IDBioPharm Consulting LLC
data.meta_description: Experience: IDBioPharm Consulting LLC · Location: Gloucester · 500+ connections on LinkedIn. View Anthony Quinn’s profile on LinkedIn, a professional community of 1 billion members.
data.text:
“Anthony is a terrific scientist, a thought leader and very valuable and importnant senior pharma executive who can enhance any organisation where he can bring these different diverse skills to bear to create real value for the business.”

“Anthony Quinn is an outstanding expert in pharma R&D and particularly in the area of translational medicine. His inquisitive approach to scientific and clinical challenges is both feared and admired - he leaves no stone unturned. Based on his thorough analysis, he works with his teams and experts to create detailed "fit for purpose" solutions, which are always based on excellent science and logic. His enthusiasm for excellence in drug discovery and development is incredibly refreshing. It has always been truly inspiring to work with Anthony.”
